data.description: Turn Key! Gorgeous Murrieta Pool home, WITH SOLAR, in time for spring!! Welcome to this stunning residence nestled in the heart of Murrieta. This meticulously maintained home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, featuring four bedrooms and three bathrooms across a spacious floor plan. As you enter, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light that illuminates the tastefully designed interiors. This home offers a main floor bedroom and bath, perfect for in-law living. On the main floor there is also an "office space" that could be an additional downstairs bedroom conversion, as well as a huge loft (potential for bedroom conversion) upstairs. The flow of this home is perfect for gatherings, holidays or any event. The kitchen boasts a large center island, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space, with an open concept floorplan feel. Your primary retreat is thoughtfully placed on the secondary level with privacy, space and a luxurious bathroom with walk in shower and soaking tub, and a private balcony with beautiful views! The 2nd level also offers 2 additional large bedrooms, plus a spacious loft (or ability for a 4th upstairs bedrooms). Don't forget the outdoor space; a true backyard oasis, where relaxation and entertainment converge. The highlight of this home is the beautifully refinished pool, inviting you to cool off on warm days or host memorable gatherings with friends and family. The meticulously landscaped yard provides a picturesque backdrop for outdoor activities, offering a perfect balance of tranquility and recreation. Whether you're lounging on the patio, taking a refreshing dip in the pool, or enjoying the lush greenery, the backyard is a private retreat that elevates the overall living experience. Convenience meets luxury with this property's prime location in Murrieta, known for its excellent schools, parks, and proximity to shopping and dining destinations. With its tasteful design, spacious layout, and a backyard that epitomizes California living don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream residence in the heart of Murrieta.
